      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ALL ON AL (1) turned in a modest effort most recently when sixth at Casino over 411m behind Steely Dawn (24.10) in a Grade 5. Some good form is emerging from his last run. Can atone. WHISPERING JACK (8) was game in defeat at the latest run, finishing third and beaten 2 lengths (20.40) behind Dad's Boys at this track. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings four times from eight starts. Hard to beat again. IN THE RHYTHM (2) turned in a better run last time to find a minor placing (24.08) at Casino behind Jimary Freedom in a Grade 5. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. Safe beginner who has drawn to advantage. Can measure up. SHE SAID SO (7) gets a chance to improve on an unplaced run at her latest outing at this circuit.",
